sign was purposeful then it is malicious). That drop adds nothing to gameplay, offers no reward, and is only there as a &quot;gotcha&quot; for unsuspecting players that happen by along a high traffic path and misstep. Any &quot;attractions&quot; at the bottom (which I have never seen myself) that lure unsuspecting players to go take a look so that they can then lose all their gear is frankly pathetic on VI's part. This is not some high (or even midlevel) zone, this is the newbie zone of Paineel. Additionally, it is not a simple drop where you fall and die and then must return to do a CR, it is a drop into a high level zone where many of us are guaranteed to not be able to access our corpse. Just my two coppers worth.<br>
<br>
